	* src/Exscript/FooLib/Interact.py: Fix: Asking a username now works when the
	USER environment variable is not set.
	* src/Exscript/Interpreter/stdlib/Connection/auto_authorize.py: Fix a
	deadlock.
	* src/Exscript/TerminalActions/LoggedSequence.py: Fix: Only create an error
	log file if an error occured. Flush logfiles regularly. Log exceptions with
	tracebacks.
	* src/Exscript/FooLib/UrlParser.py, src/Exscript/TerminalActions/Connect.py,
	src/Exscript/Exscript.py: Add support for specifying a port number using URL
	style hostnames.
